PrecisAcceptance of an instrument (Revocation of Surrender) duly approved by the members of the BIRDTAIL SIOUX BAND OF INDIANS which revokes a 1953 surrender whereby some 320 acres of Birdtail Creek Indian Reserve No. 57, in the Province of Manitoba, were surrendered by the Band for leasing to third party interests.
